<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti samastapraśasti sa 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>hitaṁbuna śrīmanmahā 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>maṁḍalēśvara velanāṁṭi 
<lb n="4"/>kulōtuṁgacōḍagoṁka 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>rājula śrīpadapadmōpajī 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>vi yamaḍāla dūbāḍaśā 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>sanuṁḍu kasaviya vedura 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ya śakavarṣamulu 1077 
<lb n="9"/>yagu nēṁṭi yuttarāyana sa 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ṁkrāṁttinimittamunaṁ dama ta 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>lli kosanāsānikiṁ daṁḍri yeṟi 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>yamanāyakunakunu<unclear>ṁ da</unclear> 
<lb n="13" break="no"/>nakunu dharmmārtthamu 
<lb n="14"/>gā śrīrāmīśvaradēvara 
<lb n="15"/>kācaṁdrārkka makhaṁḍavartti 
<lb n="16"/>diviyalakuṁ beṭṭina go 
<lb n="17" break="no"/>ṟiyalu 55 vīniṁ jēko 
<lb n="18" break="no"/>ni maḍabōyanini manmaṁḍu 
<lb n="19"/>kāṭakabrammaya dana pu 
<lb n="20" break="no"/>trānupautrikamu nitya māne 
<lb n="21" break="no"/>ṁḍu nēyu vōyaṁgalavāṁḍu 
<lb n="22"/>velanāṁṭi gōkaya <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="23"/>nellaṁgū <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="24"/>kalayaṁttakuṁ <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="25"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> ku <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> veluṁgaṁ <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="26"/>nulu <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> ṁḍunu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
</p>

